  "Start the emission of electrons": "",
  "Stop the most energetic ejected electrons": "",
  "Accelerate the electrons": "",
  "Increase the intensity of light": "",
  "The stopping potential (V0) is the minimum reverse voltage needed to stop all photoelectrons: eV0 = KE_max = hf - phi.": "",
