  "What is a photoelectron?": "",
  "An electron inside a photon under most circumstances involving energy": "",
  "A photon that acts like an electron, based on conventional assumptions about energy": "",
  "A particle found only in metals when considering all relevant energy factors": "",
  "An electron ejected from a material's surface by incident electromagnetic radiation through the photoelectric effect": "",
  "A photoelectron is an electron that has been emitted from a material through the photoelectric effect. Its kinetic energy depends on the photon's energy and the material's work function.": "",
